7
00:00:15,100 --> 00:00:16,200
她不再是小女孩了
She's not a little girl anymore.

8
00:00:16,220 --> 00:00:19,350
汉娜穿的紫色衣服 是什么意思
The purple color Hannah was wearing, what does it mean?

9
